room_title: Escape room "The Collection" by Puzzled Escape Rooms in Fargo
review: Unique idea for a fun date night or entertaining time out with a group of friends. The madam Zella's room was very fun yet still challenging enough to keep us on edge. Excited to see what is next!

room_title: Escape room "The Collection" by Puzzled Escape Rooms in Fargo
review: Had a great time solving the mystery at Madam Zella's Psychic Parlour! The puzzle was engaging and fun, challenging but not too challenging. We were a big and age-diverse group and everyone was able to contribute to solving the puzzles. I would definitely recommend for groups of all ages!
